Package: esaora
Type: Package
Title: RStudio Addin to insert " = ".
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Patrick Sturm
Maintainer: Patrick Sturm <sturm@tofwerk.com>
Description: The esaora package (Equal Sign Assignment Operator RStudio Addin)
    provides a RStudio addin which inserts " = " at the cursor position.
    The addin can be bound to a keyboard shortcut (e.g. Alt+- to replace the 
    Rstudio shortcut for " <- ").
License: GPL-3
Imports: rstudioapi (>= 0.4)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
